{"tid":1848350,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[引用] 暫停自由行簽證 = 現有簽左證嘅可以繼續輸入病毒","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T14:20:30.000Z","uid":149188,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08897c54c885910eb13ca19f1677562d5f51b127","tid":1848350,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:01:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再比佢啲語言偽術玩</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">佢話<ins><strong>暫停</strong></ins>咋 <br />\n冇話依家果啲唔嚟得</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">仲有封關唔封<strong><ins>羅湖落馬洲</ins></strong>有撚用！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥今日在記者會上宣布，要大幅減少中港兩地人員流動，減少非必要往來，第一要源頭做起，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫停發出自由行簽證</span></span>。第二，大幅縮減交通服務，西九高鐵站，紅磡直通車暫停，海運跨境航班暫停服務等。林鄭又宣布，暫停西九龍高鐵站、紅磡站、沙頭角客運等口岸運作， 措施將會 1 月 30 日（周四）凌晨生效&hellip;<br />\nㅤ<br />\nSource: 立場報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2vuckSD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2vuckSD&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=cd098074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2vuckSD</a>"},{"pid":"d6bfd76338990ab7cf38c61281ad9fa2418651cf","tid":1848350,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54f56e574d8851c8862864be11fd95e4fb494817","tid":1848350,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:01:56.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7ace21e1e72d0722eccf39549651b3f66b15b324","tid":1848350,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:02:16.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"5dbf7a917df4dc9d239fe9b472fac9555f457d11","tid":1848350,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:02:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"0a3bd5d4c50ebac44a19f820b0cefeca7889c346","tid":1848350,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited